<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Divasa Fresh – Farmers to Family</title>

<meta name="description" content="Divasa Fresh is an Indian farm-to-market fresh produce supply company delivering responsibly sourced vegetables and fruits with operational reliability.">

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
:root {
  --green:#2f6f4e;
  --light:#f5f7f6;
  --text:#1f2933;
  --muted:#6b7280;
  --border:#e5e7eb;
}

*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}

body{
  font-family:Inter, sans-serif;
  color:var(--text);
  line-height:1.6;
}

header{
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:16px 20px;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:12px;
}

header img{height:42px}

.hero{
  background:
    linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.45),rgba(0,0,0,.45)),
    url("hero.jpg") center/cover no-repeat;
  color:#fff;
  text-align:center;
  padding:100px 20px;
}

.hero h1{font-size:36px;margin-bottom:10px}
.hero p{font-size:18px;opacity:.95}

.container{
  max-width:1100px;
  margin:auto;
  padding:60px 20px;
}

h2{font-size:26px;margin-bottom:14px}
p{color:var(--muted);max-width:850px}

.grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));
  gap:30px;
  margin-top:30px;
}

.card{
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:6px;
  overflow:hidden;
  background:#fff;
}

.card img{
  width:100%;
  height:180px;
  object-fit:cover;
}

.card div{padding:18px}
.card h3{color:var(--green);margin-bottom:6px}

.steps{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));
  gap:20px;
  margin-top:20px;
}

.step{
  border-left:4px solid var(--green);
  padding-left:14px;
  color:var(--muted);
}

form{
  max-width:600px;
  margin-top:30px;
}

input,select,textarea{
  width:100%;
  padding:12px;
  margin-bottom:14px;
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:4px;
}

button{
  background:var(--green);
  color:#fff;
  border:none;
  padding:12px 26px;
  font-size:16px;
  border-radius:4px;
  cursor:pointer;
}

footer{
  background:var(--light);
  padding:40px 20px;
  font-size:14px;
  color:var(--muted);
}

@media(max-width:600px){
  .hero h1{font-size:28px}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <!-- Uncomment after uploading logo -->
  <!-- <img src="logo.png" alt="Divasa Fresh Logo"> -->
  <strong>Divasa Fresh – Farmers to Family</strong>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <h1>Farm-sourced produce, delivered with integrity.</h1>
  <p>Reliable farm-to-market fresh produce supply</p>
</section>

<section class="container">
  <h2>About Divasa Fresh</h2>
  <p>
    Divasa Fresh is an Indian fresh produce supply company working with partner farms to
    deliver vegetables and fruits through structured sourcing, quality checks, and
    disciplined logistics.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="container">
  <h2>Vision & Mission</h2>
  <p><strong>Vision:</strong> To be a trusted farm-to-market supply partner across India.</p>
  <p><strong>Mission:</strong> To operate a reliable, quality-led produce supply system for households and businesses.</p>
</section>

<section class="container">
  <h2>Our Services</h2>

  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="sourcing.jpg" alt="Farm sourcing">
      <div>
        <h3>Farm Sourcing</h3>
        <p>Planned procurement through long-term farmer partnerships.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="quality.jpg" alt="Quality assurance">
      <div>
        <h3>Quality Assurance</h3>
        <p>Sorting, grading, and hygiene-focused handling standards.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="delivery.jpg" alt="Delivery">
      <div>
        <h3>Supply & Delivery</h3>
        <p>Predictable fulfillment for households, retail, and HORECA.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container">
  <h2>How It Works</h2>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">Farm-level planning</div>
    <div class="step">Aggregation & grading</div>
    <div class="step">Order alignment</div>
    <div class="step">Timely delivery</div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container">
  <h2>Business Enquiry</h2>
  <form>
    <input placeholder="Name" required>
    <input placeholder="Company / Household / Business Type" required>
    <input placeholder="Contact Number" required>
    <input type="email" placeholder="Email" required>
    <input placeholder="Location" required>

    <select required>
      <option value="">Enquiry Type</option>
      <option>Household</option>
      <option>Retail</option>
      <option>HORECA</option>
    </select>

    <textarea rows="3" placeholder="Message"></textarea>
    <button type="submit">Submit Enquiry</button>
  </form>
</section>

<section class="container">
  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +91-XXXXXXXXXX</p>
  <p><strong>Email:</strong> contact@divasafresh.com</p>
  <p><strong>Operating Hours:</strong> 7:00 AM – 12:00 PM | 4:00 PM – 8:00 PM</p>
</section>

<footer>
  <p><strong>Divasa Fresh – Farmers to Family</strong></p>
  <p>Responsible sourcing • Quality discipline • Reliable operations</p>
  <p>© Divasa Fresh. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
